269
00:18:33,067 --> 00:18:40,033
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

270
00:18:52,667 --> 00:18:59,033
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

271
00:19:06,967 --> 00:19:08,100
What?

272
00:19:08,800 --> 00:19:10,167
This is what you wanted, right?

273
00:19:13,967 --> 00:19:15,267
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

274
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:17,267
You think I was bluffing?

275
00:19:20,267 --> 00:19:23,367
You think I wasn't serious
about killing myself?

276
00:19:24,900 --> 00:19:26,033
Tell me!

277
00:19:30,433 --> 00:19:32,067
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

278
00:19:32,167 --> 00:19:33,633
[SAMUEL]
 Is this a test?

279
00:19:33,767 --> 00:19:36,300
Are they really just going
to watch me die?

280
00:19:37,267 --> 00:19:39,800
No, I don't think so.

281
00:19:39,933 --> 00:19:43,367
They won't risk losing the only
 man who holds the key

282
00:19:43,500 --> 00:19:44,900
to getting their money back.

283
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:46,800
They're just trying
to call my bluff.

284
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:49,367
But if I ever miscalculated...

285
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:50,767
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

286
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:53,800
Ma, I hope you can forgive me.

287
00:19:55,767 --> 00:19:57,467
Son, I'm so sorry.

288
00:19:58,833 --> 00:20:00,600
I love you so much, King.

289
00:20:05,867 --> 00:20:11,333
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

290
00:20:11,500 --> 00:20:12,400
[GUNSHOT]

291
00:20:15,533 --> 00:20:18,000
We have to be more careful
than ever.

292
00:20:18,133 --> 00:20:20,167
Agnes, let's meet at the park.

293
00:20:20,833 --> 00:20:22,300
We need to talk.

294
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:27,267
You're playing my own men
like pawns.

295
00:20:27,367 --> 00:20:33,333
They're fired up
and unstoppable.

296
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:34,967
- Let's spar?
- Sure.

297
00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:36,433
I know he's fuming with rage.

298
00:20:36,567 --> 00:20:40,700
I've got the upper hand against
 him and his brother.

